{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":869,"text":"Are you tired of your boss?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":3073,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":4453,"text":"Are you tired of going to work"},{"time":6318,"text":"and making money for other people?"},{"time":9965,"text":"And who are those people anyways?"},{"time":11565,"text":"Those people that make\nmoney from your work."},{"time":14378,"text":"Well, they're capitalists."},{"time":16300,"text":"They have capital,"},{"time":17600,"text":"and they use your labor\nto make more capital."},{"time":20973,"text":"So if you're tired of going to work"},{"time":23071,"text":"and making money for other people,"},{"time":25300,"text":"then you're probably like me --"},{"time":26992,"text":"just tired of capitalism."},{"time":29801,"text":"Which is ironic, because I'm a capitalist."}]},{"cues":[{"time":32847,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":34289,"text":"I own a small business --"},{"time":36036,"text":"Rco Tires in Compton."},{"time":38584,"text":"A few years ago, when I read Van Jones,"},{"time":40571,"text":"and he wrote, \"Let's make\ngreen collar jobs in the hood,\""},{"time":43513,"text":"I took him really seriously."},{"time":46088,"text":"So I cofounded, own and operate\na tire recycling company,"},{"time":49812,"text":"and I'm really proud of what we've done."},{"time":51798,"text":"So far, we've recycled\na hundred million pounds of rubber."},{"time":55582,"text":"That's 21 million gallons of oil\ndiverted from landfills"},{"time":59631,"text":"into new products."}]},{"cues":[{"time":61235,"text":"(Cheers)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":62409,"text":"We also employ about 15 guys --"},{"time":64648,"text":"mostly people of color,"},{"time":66221,"text":"most of whom are felons,"},{"time":67615,"text":"and we pay above the minimum wage,"},{"time":69514,"text":"and we are now proud members\nof the United Steelworkers Union."}]},{"cues":[{"time":72948,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":78531,"text":"Now, Rco is not a cooperative now."},{"time":81094,"text":"It's a privately held company\nwith community-minded ownership,"},{"time":84785,"text":"but I would like it to become one."},{"time":86563,"text":"I would like for them to fire the boss --"},{"time":88882,"text":"that's me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":90245,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":91317,"text":"And I'm going to tell you why,"},{"time":92787,"text":"but first, let me tell you\nhow we got started."},{"time":95863,"text":"So a lot of people ask,"},{"time":97037,"text":"\"How did Rco come to be?\""},{"time":98495,"text":"And I have to be really honest."},{"time":100419,"text":"I leveraged my white privilege."},{"time":102764,"text":"So, here's how white privilege\nworked for me and Rco."},{"time":107448,"text":"My white grandmother\nwas born on her family's plantation"},{"time":111317,"text":"in Arkansas in 1918."},{"time":113995,"text":"She traveled with her white father west,"},{"time":116949,"text":"following the oil boom."},{"time":118542,"text":"And he held various union oil jobs --"},{"time":121746,"text":"jobs which would have never been given\nto my black great-grandfather,"},{"time":125231,"text":"had he lived here at the time."},{"time":127742,"text":"Granny became a hairdresser"},{"time":129695,"text":"and then got a loan with her husband"},{"time":133624,"text":"who built their home\nin West Los Angeles --"},{"time":135718,"text":"a loan which would never have been\ngiven to a black family at the time."},{"time":140421,"text":"And after my grandfather passed away,"},{"time":142281,"text":"my granny was able to keep that house"},{"time":144084,"text":"because she had his pension\nand his health care"},{"time":146785,"text":"from a state job which he held,"},{"time":148577,"text":"which again, would have never been\ngiven to a black man"},{"time":151223,"text":"before the anti-discrimination\nact of the 1960s."}]},{"cues":[{"time":154048,"text":"So, you fast-forward 30 years,"},{"time":155930,"text":"and I graduate,"},{"time":157342,"text":"and I want to start my own business"},{"time":159068,"text":"with a pile of debt and a credit card,"},{"time":160969,"text":"and no experience in the tire industry."},{"time":163336,"text":"But I had what most people didn't have."},{"time":165597,"text":"I had a clean, safe, free place to live."},{"time":171036,"text":"I moved in with my grandmother,"},{"time":172808,"text":"and I was able to rent\nour first warehouse,"},{"time":175157,"text":"buy our first truck,"},{"time":176357,"text":"pay our first employees,"},{"time":177941,"text":"because I didn't have to worry\nabout paying myself,"},{"time":180379,"text":"because I didn't need to feed myself,"},{"time":182186,"text":"because I am the direct beneficiary\nof generations of white privilege."}]},{"cues":[{"time":186703,"text":"Now, telling the story\nof white privilege is important"},{"time":190791,"text":"because very often people say,"},{"time":192244,"text":"\"Oh, we want more companies like yours."},{"time":194126,"text":"We want more Rco's,"},{"time":195308,"text":"we want more black-owned businesses,"},{"time":197181,"text":"female-led, triple bottom line,"},{"time":199869,"text":"Ban the Box,"},{"time":201065,"text":"green manufacturing companies,\" right?"},{"time":203739,"text":"But the question we have to ask is,\nwhere is the wealth?"},{"time":206406,"text":"Where is the money?"},{"time":207581,"text":"Where's the capital in our communities"},{"time":209471,"text":"to build the types\nof businesses that we want?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":211654,"text":"And in telling a story\nof the white side of my family,"},{"time":214226,"text":"I needed a dozen ways"},{"time":215401,"text":"where blacks were excluded\nfrom the economy,"},{"time":217486,"text":"whereas the white side of my family\nwas able to gain access and traction,"},{"time":221058,"text":"and build wealth ..."},{"time":223224,"text":"Primarily because racism\nand capitalism are best homies, but --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":227858,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":229684,"text":"but what that means\nis that when we ask ourselves,"},{"time":232161,"text":"\"Why are our communities broke?\" --"},{"time":234646,"text":"Like, we're not just broke\nbecause we're broke;"},{"time":236876,"text":"we're broke for a reason."},{"time":238235,"text":"Historical context really does matter."}]},{"cues":[{"time":241710,"text":"But our history\ntells another story as well."},{"time":243885,"text":"There's this incredible book\ncalled \"Collective Courage,\""},{"time":246597,"text":"which is the story of how\nthousands of African Americans"},{"time":249837,"text":"have been able to build\nbusinesses and schools,"},{"time":252381,"text":"hospitals, farming cooperatives,"},{"time":254648,"text":"banks, financial institutions --"},{"time":256389,"text":"entire communities\nand sovereign economies,"},{"time":259025,"text":"without a lot of capital."},{"time":261037,"text":"And they did it by working together"},{"time":262978,"text":"and leveraging their community assets"},{"time":265409,"text":"and trusting each other"},{"time":266885,"text":"and putting solidarity first --"},{"time":268609,"text":"not just profits by any means necessary."},{"time":272381,"text":"And they didn't have to wait around\nfor celebrities and athletes"},{"time":275717,"text":"to bring their money back to the hood."},{"time":278027,"text":"However, if you are\na celebrity or an athlete,"},{"time":280206,"text":"and you're listening to this,"},{"time":281623,"text":"please feel free to bring your money."}]},{"cues":[{"time":283433,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":286031,"text":"But they did it\nthrough cooperative economics,"},{"time":288291,"text":"because they knew"},{"time":289466,"text":"that capitalism was never\ngoing to finance black liberation."},{"time":292943,"text":"So, there are so many great\nexamples in this book,"},{"time":296994,"text":"and I suggest that everybody just read it"},{"time":299117,"text":"because it answers\nthe question I asked earlier,"},{"time":301384,"text":"which was where are we going\nto get the wealth"},{"time":303712,"text":"to build the types\nof business that we want."},{"time":305812,"text":"And the answer is going to have\nto be cooperative economics."}]},{"cues":[{"time":308684,"text":"There's a lot of different\nversions of cooperativism."},{"time":311668,"text":"What I'm talking about today\nis worker ownership."},{"time":314684,"text":"You may not have heard\nof worker ownership,"},{"time":316717,"text":"but it's been an incredible tool"},{"time":318351,"text":"for black economic liberation\nfor a century,"},{"time":320456,"text":"and it's also working\nall over the world right now."},{"time":323528,"text":"You may have heard of Black Wall Street"},{"time":325470,"text":"or maybe the Zapatistas,"},{"time":326685,"text":"but I'll give you an example\nthat's a little bit closer to home."},{"time":329755,"text":"Right now, today, in South Bronx,"},{"time":332296,"text":"is the country's largest\nworker-owned company."},{"time":335517,"text":"It's called Cooperative\nHome Care Associates,"},{"time":338210,"text":"and it was founded by black\nand Latinx home care workers"},{"time":341194,"text":"who are now able\nto pay themselves living wages,"},{"time":344291,"text":"they have full-time hours,"},{"time":345570,"text":"they have benefits and a pension,"},{"time":347222,"text":"through their membership\nas a unit of SEIU."},{"time":350778,"text":"And these women owners now receive\na dividend back on their ownership"},{"time":354650,"text":"every year that the company\nhas been profitable,"},{"time":356967,"text":"which has been most years."},{"time":358989,"text":"So they're able to really enjoy\nthe fruits of their labor"},{"time":362934,"text":"because they fired the boss."},{"time":365299,"text":"They don't have any big investors."},{"time":366992,"text":"They don't have fat-cat CEOs"},{"time":368624,"text":"or absentee owners taking\nthe profit out of the company."},{"time":372137,"text":"They each pay in\nabout 1,000 dollars over time"},{"time":376054,"text":"in order to gain ownership,"},{"time":377994,"text":"and now they own their job."}]},{"cues":[{"time":380598,"text":"Now, there's hundreds of more examples\nof companies like this"},{"time":383607,"text":"springing up all across the country."},{"time":385465,"text":"And I'm so inspired by what they're doing,"},{"time":388738,"text":"because it really represents\nan alternative"},{"time":391247,"text":"to the type of economy we have now,"},{"time":393302,"text":"which exploits all of us."},{"time":395319,"text":"It also represents an alternative"},{"time":396994,"text":"to waiting around for big investors\nto bring chain stores,"},{"time":400978,"text":"or big-box stores to our communities,"},{"time":402774,"text":"because honestly,\nthose types of developments,"},{"time":405074,"text":"they steal resources from our communities."},{"time":407422,"text":"They put our mom-and-pop shops\nout of business,"},{"time":410283,"text":"they make our entrepreneurs\ninto wage workers,"},{"time":413403,"text":"and they take money out of our pocket"},{"time":415233,"text":"and send it to their shareholders."}]},{"cues":[{"time":418031,"text":"So, I was so inspired by all these stories\nof resistance and resilience"},{"time":421455,"text":"that I got together with a few people\nhere in Los Angeles,"},{"time":424247,"text":"and we created LUCI."},{"time":425995,"text":"LUCI stands for the Los Angeles\nUnion Cooperative Initiative,"},{"time":430194,"text":"and our objective is to create\nmore worker-owned businesses"},{"time":433314,"text":"here in Los Angeles."},{"time":435004,"text":"So far, in the last year,\nwe've created two:"},{"time":437386,"text":"Pacific Electric, an electrical company,"},{"time":439403,"text":"and Vermont Gage Carwash,"},{"time":440982,"text":"which is right here in South-Central,"},{"time":442769,"text":"some of you guys\nmight be familiar with it."},{"time":444825,"text":"This long-time carwash is now owned\nand operated by its 20 workers,"},{"time":449520,"text":"all of whom are union members as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":451568,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":456828,"text":"So you might be wondering\nwhy the focus on union-worker ownership,"},{"time":460750,"text":"but there's a lot of good reasons"},{"time":462401,"text":"why the labor movement is a natural ally\nto the worker-ownership movement."},{"time":466175,"text":"To build these companies\nthat we want in our community,"},{"time":468795,"text":"we need a few things."},{"time":469970,"text":"We're going to need money,\npeople and training."},{"time":473000,"text":"Unions have all of those things."},{"time":475880,"text":"America's working class has been\npaying union dues for decades,"},{"time":478871,"text":"and with it, our unions have been building"},{"time":480943,"text":"dignified, decent,\nand democratic workplaces for us."},{"time":483801,"text":"However, union jobs\nare on the steep decline,"},{"time":486250,"text":"and it's time for us to start\ncalling on our unions"},{"time":488680,"text":"to really bring all of their financial\nand political capital"},{"time":492369,"text":"to bear in the creation of new,\nunion, living-wage jobs"},{"time":496076,"text":"in our communities."},{"time":497873,"text":"Also, union halls\nare full of union members"},{"time":501128,"text":"who understand\nthe importance of solidarity"},{"time":504295,"text":"and the power of collective action."},{"time":507328,"text":"These are the types of folks that want\nmore union businesses to exist,"},{"time":511781,"text":"so let's build them with them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":515247,"text":"Learning from our unions,"},{"time":516534,"text":"learning from our past,"},{"time":517709,"text":"learning from our peers,"},{"time":518906,"text":"are all going to be very\nimportant to our success,"},{"time":521574,"text":"which is why I'd like to leave you\nwith one last example"},{"time":524502,"text":"and a vision for the future ..."},{"time":527153,"text":"and that vision is Mondragon, Spain."},{"time":530485,"text":"Mondragon, Spain is a community\nbuilt entirely around worker cooperatives."},{"time":535701,"text":"There's 260-plus businesses here,"},{"time":538686,"text":"manufacturing everything from bicycles\nto washing machines to transformers."},{"time":544046,"text":"And this group of businesses\nnow employs 80,000 people"},{"time":547586,"text":"and earns more than 12 billion euros\nin revenue every year."},{"time":551421,"text":"And all of the companies there\nare owned by the people that work in them."},{"time":555896,"text":"They've also built universities\nand hospitals and financial institutions."},{"time":560636,"text":"I mean, imagine if we could build\nsomething like this in South-Central."},{"time":565839,"text":"The late mayor of Jackson\nhad a similar idea."},{"time":569565,"text":"He wanted to turn his entire city\ninto a Mondragon-like cooperative economy,"},{"time":575017,"text":"calling his ambitious plan\n\"Jackson Rising.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":578940,"text":"And when I look at Mondragon,"},{"time":580390,"text":"I see really what working-class people\ncan do for ourselves"},{"time":583224,"text":"when we work together"},{"time":584399,"text":"and make decisions\nfor ourselves and each other"},{"time":586979,"text":"and our communities."},{"time":591516,"text":"And what's really incredible\nabout Mondragon"},{"time":594519,"text":"is that while we are dreaming about them,"},{"time":597010,"text":"they are dreaming about us."},{"time":599465,"text":"This community in Spain has decided\nto launch an international initiative"},{"time":604349,"text":"to create more communities\nlike it all over the world,"},{"time":607375,"text":"by linking up with unions,"},{"time":609006,"text":"by supporting organizations like LUCI,"},{"time":610943,"text":"and by educating folks\nabout the worker-ownership model."}]},{"cues":[{"time":615357,"text":"Now, here's what you can do\nto be a part of it."},{"time":617896,"text":"If you're a union member,\ngo to your union meetings,"},{"time":620500,"text":"and make sure that your union\nhas a worker-ownership initiative,"},{"time":623714,"text":"and become a part of it."},{"time":625357,"text":"If you're an entrepreneur,"},{"time":626655,"text":"if you have a small business,"},{"time":628099,"text":"or you're interested in starting one,"},{"time":629942,"text":"then link up with LUCI\nor another organization like us"},{"time":632633,"text":"to help you get started\non the cooperative model."},{"time":635258,"text":"If you're a politician,"},{"time":636434,"text":"or you work for one,"},{"time":637850,"text":"or you just like talking to them,"},{"time":639541,"text":"please get the city, state, federal\nand county legislation passed"},{"time":643802,"text":"that we need in order to fund\nand support worker-owned businesses."}]},{"cues":[{"time":647987,"text":"And for everybody else,"},{"time":649244,"text":"learn about our history,\nlearn about our models,"},{"time":651507,"text":"and seek us out so can support us,"},{"time":653157,"text":"you can buy from us, invest in us,\nlend to us and join us,"},{"time":656388,"text":"because it's really\ngoing to take all of us"},{"time":658478,"text":"in order to build the more just\nand sustainable and resilient economy"},{"time":662122,"text":"that we want for ourselves\nand our children."}]},{"cues":[{"time":665859,"text":"And with that,"},{"time":667112,"text":"I would like to leave you\nwith a quote from Arundhati Roy,"},{"time":670327,"text":"and she writes ..."},{"time":672547,"text":"\"Our strategy should not be only\nto confront Empire,"},{"time":676722,"text":"but to lay siege to it."},{"time":679196,"text":"To deprive it of oxygen."},{"time":681729,"text":"To mock it."},{"time":683119,"text":"To shame it."},{"time":684881,"text":"With our art,"},{"time":686120,"text":"our literature,"},{"time":687318,"text":"our music,"},{"time":688606,"text":"our brilliance,"},{"time":690311,"text":"our joy,"},{"time":692153,"text":"our sheer relentlessness --"},{"time":694574,"text":"and our ability to tell our own stories."},{"time":697206,"text":"Not the stories that we're being\nbrainwashed to believe."},{"time":701729,"text":"The corporate revolution will collapse"},{"time":703822,"text":"if we refuse to buy\nwhat they're selling --"},{"time":707236,"text":"their ideas,"},{"time":708719,"text":"their version of history,"},{"time":710351,"text":"their wars,"},{"time":711526,"text":"their weapons,"},{"time":713324,"text":"their sense of inevitability."},{"time":715956,"text":"Because know this:"},{"time":717804,"text":"They be few and we be many."},{"time":720233,"text":"They need us more than we need them."},{"time":723136,"text":"Another world is not only possible,"},{"time":725722,"text":"she's on her way."},{"time":727657,"text":"And on a quiet day,"},{"time":729452,"text":"I can hear her breathing.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":731328,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":732503,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}